Skills.Name: Noble Mind
Skills.Description: Raises own DEF by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 10s. Further grants ongoing HP recovery by 15% of DEF for 15s. Inflicts Provoke on all enemies for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises own DEF, grants ongoing HP recovery. Inflicts Provoke on all enemies

Skills.Name: Glistening Blade
Skills.Description: Inflicts (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's DEF) DMG on all enemies and lowers DEF by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 20s. Also raises DMG Received by <color=red>{3}%</color>. Further reduces DEF by <color=red>{2}%</color> and raises DMG Received by <color=red>{4}%</color> if Red Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts DMG, lowers DEF, raises DMG Received on all enemies. Reduces DEF, raises DMG Received if Red Elemental

Skills.Name: Going Beyond
Skills.Description: Raises DEF of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 10s. Inflicts (<color=red>{1}%</color> of skill user's DEF) DMG on single enemy. Recovers own HP by <color=red>{2}%</color> of DEF.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises DEF of all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy. Recovers own HP

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Reduces DMG Received for all allies by <color=red>5.00%-40.00%</color> for 5s according to Combo Bonus. Further shields DMG (<color=red>80.00%-200.00%</color> of skill user's DEF) for 10s. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Reduces DMG Received for all allies, shields DMG. Inflicts DMG on single enemy
